Happy Gut = Happy Life 💕

Our gut health affects every organ of our body, that’s why it’s so important to do everything we can to have a healthy gut. 

Here are some things I do every single day to do so! 

🥦Consume a variety of fruits, vegetables, whole grains, and legumes to provide essential nutrients and fiber that support a healthy gut.
🧘🏾‍♀️I started doing yoga, and every day Incorporate poses that are good for my gut. The practice of yoga also promotes relaxation, which can positively influence gut health by reducing stress.
💦I drink tons of water! I’ve been drinking a gallon a day for a couple of years now and it makes such a difference. Hydration is crucial for nutrient absorption and promoting a healthy gut lining.
💊 I take supplements like Berberine Phytosome by @enzymedica to support my metabolism. Metabolism is responsible for converting the food we eat into energy. Using Berberine Phytosome helps me achieve a properly functioning metabolism to the integrity of my gut lining.
PLUS, it helps curb my cravings which allows me to be more mindful of the food I eat 😍💕
